data.text:
One of the chirpiest, vivacious, the most beautiful and loved actresses from Indian television fraternity, Sanaya Irani shattered millions of hearts when she took the wedding vows with long-time boyfriend and actor, Mohit Sehgal. They both met at the sets of Miley Jab Hum Tum and fell for each other right away.

After dating for almost five years (probably more than that), they finally decided to take their relation a step ahead. And so, they walked down the aisle on January 25, 2016 in Goa. If you missed the lovely wedding story of theirs that we shared with you earlier, check it out right here!

advertisement

Ever since these lovebirds tied the knot, they are vacay mode. After enjoying a holiday in Spain and exploring the beautiful pace hand-in-hand, the duo has recently been on a vacation in Singapore. And trust they had an amazing time there. Wondering how can we say so? Boy, we have digital proof of it and they are saying it all!

advertisement

You all might know, Mohit and Sanaya have recently joined Instagram. They keep sharing pictures on their respective profiles to stay in touch with their fans (and that’s what social media is all about).
